data.value: Maintaing data is a very important part of Computer Science.For my Final project of this class I decided to work on a databased base application.This program is intented to be used by Store Managers to keep track of sales and profit made by each Product which is helpful for the managers to understand what product customers like the most or what should be ordered next.The pograme stores the Databse of the inventory listed in a order of Quantity Sold and Profit Earned by each item. The user can also add or delete product from the database.I had a lot of fun working on this project. Thank you so much to Professor Sunmonno for working so hard to tach us.
